n Zirkulation, das in der frühen Kybernetik zum funktionalen Kernstück eines »neuronalen« Gedächtnismodells in Mensch und Maschine aufstieg.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aGedächtnismodell. 4aGeschichte des 20. Jahrhunderts. 4aGeschichtswissenschaft. 4aInformatik. 4aJohn Von Neumann. 4aNervennetzmodelle. 4aRafael Lorente De Nó. 4aRegenerative Zirkulation. 4aTechnik. 4aTechnikgeschichte. 4aWissenschaft. 4aWissenschaftsgeschichte. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh  aComputer Sciences.  aHistory of Science.  aHistory of Technology.  aHistory of the 20th Century.  aHistory.  aTechnology.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Geschichte 2010-2013z97831103707370 cprintz978383762065840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839420652?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839420652423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839420652/original  a978-3-11-037073-7  transcript Highlight Collection Geschichte 2010-2013c2010d2013  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2010d2013